+<h2>Published-Content Search Facets</h2>
+<p>Browse the existing local search index by genuine content type. Counts are calculated in your browser from published JSON records and the public route directory.</p>
+<p>No query, preference or interaction is sent to a remote AI, analytics service or account system.</p>
+</section>
+
+<section class="facet-summary-grid" aria-label="Published search summary">
+<article class="card facet-summary"><span>Published searchable records</span><strong id="facetTotal">…</strong></article>
+<article class="card facet-summary"><span>Content types</span><strong id="facetTypeTotal">…</strong></article>
+<article class="card facet-summary"><span>Bounded extracts and registers</span><strong id="facetBoundedTotal">…</strong></article>
+</section>
+
+<section class="card" aria-labelledby="facet-controls-heading">
+<h2 id="facet-controls-heading">Filter published records</h2>
+<form id="facetForm" class="facet-control-grid" role="search">
+<label for="facetQuery">Search words
+<input id="facetQuery" name="q" type="search" autocomplete="off" placeholder="பழனி, Vel, Sashti, literature…">
+</label>
+<label for="facetStatus">Publication boundary
+<select id="facetStatus" name="status">
+<option value="all">All published boundaries</option>
+<option value="published">Published or source-linked</option>
+<option value="bounded">Reviewed extract or bounded section</option>
+<option value="register">Source register</option>
+</select>
+</label>
+<button class="btn secondary" id="facetReset" type="button">Reset filters</button>
+</form>
+<div>
+<h3>Content type</h3>
