+</div>
+<p id="facetResultStatus" role="status" aria-live="polite">Loading published records…</p>
+</section>
+
+<section id="facetResults" class="grid facet-results" aria-busy="true" aria-label="Published search results">
+<article class="card">Loading the local search index…</article>
+</section>
+
+<section class="card">
+<h2>Publication boundary</h2>
+<p>Drafts, records marked not published, and records requiring source review are excluded. Source registers and reviewed extracts remain visible with their status clearly labelled because their routes are already public.</p>
